Agenda

	* What is abstraction ?
		Abstraction is a process of hiding the implementation details
		and showing only functionality to the user.

		Mainly we use for security purpose.
		Make it  simple and easy.

	* How can we achieve the abstraction in java ?

	* Implementation of abstraction ?


	Note :- 100% of abstraction can be happen in Java 1.7 using interface.
			After Java 1.7 we can accrue 100% of abstraction may be or may not be possible using interface depends on user.
			In abstract class not be accrue 100% of abstraction.